---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="fr"
  title="Blog Fitness &amp; Musculation - AIVancePro"
  description="Conseils fitness, musculation et entra&icirc;nement. D&eacute;couvrez nos articles pour optimiser vos performances sportives avec l'aide de l'IA."
  canonical="https://aivancepro.fr/blog/"
  alternates={{ fr: 'https://aivancepro.fr/blog/', en: 'https://aivancepro.fr/en/blog/', de: 'https://aivancepro.fr/de/blog/' }}
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .blog-header {
        padding: 9rem 2rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gray-50) 0%, var(--white) 100%);
      }
      .blog-header .section-label {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--blue);
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }
      .blog-header h1 {
        font-size: 2.8rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      .blog-header p {
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        max-width: 550px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .category-filter {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 2rem auto 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        padding: 0 2rem;
      }
      .filter-btn {
        padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 50px;
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        background: var(--white);
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-family: inherit;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: all 0.2s;
      }
      .filter-btn:hover, .filter-btn.active {
        background: var(--blue);
        color: var(--white);
        border-color: var(--blue);
      }
      .articles {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 3rem 2rem 6rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
        gap: 1.5rem;
      }
      .article-card {
        background: var(--white);
        border: 1px solid var(--gray-200);
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--gray-900);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .article-card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.3);
        transform: translateY(-4px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .article-card .card-image {
        width: 100%;
        height: 180px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-100), var(--gray-200));
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .article-card .card-content {
        padding: 1.5rem;
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }
      .article-card .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
        background: rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.06);
        border-radius: 50px;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        color: var(--blue);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        width: fit-content;
      }
      .article-card h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        line-height: 1.35;
      }
      .article-card p {
        color: var(--gray-500);
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        flex: 1;
      }
      .article-card .meta {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--gray-400);
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .article-card.featured {
        grid-column: 1 / -1;
        flex-direction: row;
      }
      .article-card.featured .card-image {
        width: 45%;
        height: auto;
        min-height: 250px;
      }
      .article-card.featured .card-content {
        padding: 2rem;
      }
      .article-card.featured h2 {
        font-size: 1.4rem;
      }
      .article-card.featured p {
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .blog-header h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
        .blog-header { padding: 7rem 1.5rem 2rem; }
        .articles { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        .article-card.featured { flex-direction: column; }
        .article-card.featured .card-image { width: 100%; min-height: 180px; }
      }
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <header class="blog-header">
    <div class="section-label">Blog</div>
    <h1>Fitness &amp; Musculation</h1>
    <p>Conseils, guides et astuces pour optimiser votre entra&icirc;nement et atteindre vos objectifs.</p>

    <div class="category-filter">
      <button class="filter-btn active" onclick="filterArticles('all', this)">Tous</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterArticles('ia', this)">Intelligence Artificielle</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterArticles('musculation', this)">Musculation</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterArticles('nutrition', this)">Nutrition</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterArticles('conseils', this)">Conseils</button>
      <button class="filter-btn" onclick="filterArticles('programmation', this)">Programmation</button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="articles">
    <a href="/blog/coach-ia-fitness/" class="article-card featured" data-category="ia">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Coach IA</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Intelligence Artificielle</span>
        <h2>Comment l'IA r&eacute;volutionne le coaching fitness</h2>
        <p>D&eacute;couvrez comment l'intelligence artificielle transforme l'entra&icirc;nement sportif en proposant des programmes ultra-personnalis&eacute;s adapt&eacute;s &agrave; chaque profil.</p>
        <div class="meta">7 f&eacute;vrier 2026 &middot; 5 min de lecture</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/programme-musculation-debutant/" class="article-card" data-category="musculation">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Musculation d&eacute;butant</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Musculation</span>
        <h2>Programme musculation d&eacute;butant : par o&ugrave; commencer</h2>
        <p>Vous d&eacute;butez en musculation ? Voici le guide complet pour construire votre premier programme d'entra&icirc;nement efficace.</p>
        <div class="meta">7 f&eacute;vrier 2026 &middot; 7 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/suivi-progression-sportive/" class="article-card" data-category="conseils">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Suivi progression</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Progression</span>
        <h2>L'importance du suivi de progression sportive</h2>
        <p>Pourquoi suivre sa progression est la cl&eacute; pour des r&eacute;sultats durables.</p>
        <div class="meta">7 f&eacute;vrier 2026 &middot; 5 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/motivation-sport/" class="article-card" data-category="conseils">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Motivation</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Motivation</span>
        <h2>5 astuces pour rester motiv&eacute; dans son entra&icirc;nement</h2>
        <p>La motivation est le carburant de la r&eacute;ussite sportive. 5 strat&eacute;gies concr&egrave;tes.</p>
        <div class="meta">7 f&eacute;vrier 2026 &middot; 4 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/home-gym-entrainement-maison/" class="article-card" data-category="conseils">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Home Gym</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Home Gym</span>
        <h2>S'entra&icirc;ner &agrave; la maison : guide complet</h2>
        <p>Pas besoin de salle de sport pour progresser. Cr&eacute;ez votre espace d'entra&icirc;nement.</p>
        <div class="meta">7 f&eacute;vrier 2026 &middot; 6 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/periodisation-programme-entrainement/" class="article-card" data-category="programmation">
      <div class="card-image">Photo P&eacute;riodisation</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Programmation</span>
        <h2>P&eacute;riodisation : structurer son programme</h2>
        <p>Cycles, m&eacute;socycles, deload : tout comprendre pour progresser durablement.</p>
        <div class="meta">3 mars 2026 &middot; 6 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/erreurs-musculation/" class="article-card" data-category="musculation">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Erreurs musculation</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Conseils</span>
        <h2>5 erreurs courantes en musculation</h2>
        <p>Les pi&egrave;ges fr&eacute;quents qui freinent votre progression et comment les corriger.</p>
        <div class="meta">3 mars 2026 &middot; 5 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/nutrition-musculation-bases/" class="article-card" data-category="nutrition">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Nutrition</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Nutrition</span>
        <h2>Nutrition et musculation : les bases</h2>
        <p>Prot&eacute;ines, glucides, lipides et timing des repas pour soutenir votre progression.</p>
        <div class="meta">3 mars 2026 &middot; 7 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href="/blog/choisir-exercices-objectifs/" class="article-card" data-category="musculation">
      <div class="card-image">Photo Exercices</div>
      <div class="card-content">
        <span class="tag">Exercices</span>
        <h2>Comment choisir ses exercices selon ses objectifs</h2>
        <p>Force, hypertrophie, endurance : guide pour s&eacute;lectionner les bons exercices.</p>
        <div class="meta">3 mars 2026 &middot; 6 min</div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </section>

  <script>
    function filterArticles(category, btn) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.filter-btn').forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
      btn.classList.add('active');
      document.querySelectorAll('.article-card').forEach(card => {
        if (category === 'all' || card.dataset.category === category) {
          card.style.display = '';
        } else {
          card.style.display = 'none';
        }
      });
    }
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
